Class DocsFreqBlockIndexInput.DocsFreqBlockReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sindice.siren.index.codecs.block.BlockIndexInput.BlockReader

  • Enclosing class:
    DocsFreqBlockIndexInput

    public class DocsFreqBlockIndexInput.DocsFreqBlockReader
extends BlockIndexInput.BlockReader
    Implementation of the BlockReader for the .doc file.

    Read and decode blocks containing the document identifiers and the node frequencies. It also decodes the pointers of the associated blocks from the .nod and .pos files and updates the specified Indexs.
